						<div class="postbody">The only time I've ever lost saves (on my Yobo anyway) was on Crystalis, but it only happened when my two-year-old yanked the power wart out of the wall. It only happened ten or twelve times <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" />
